
### upload
http://localhost:{{local.server.port}}/file

// [file]
@name = uploaded.csv
@path = src/test/resources/file.csv
@field = file
@mineType = text/csv

identifier = {{UUID:}}
timestamp = {{DATE_TIME:}}

// [assertions]
EQUALS_TO! 201 {{HTTP:status}}


### uploadWithoutForm
http://localhost:{{local.server.port}}/file

